    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Separation between layers, as between a paint or varnish film and other film layers, or between a film layer and its support, or separation along planes of weakness in crystalline materials.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
